Our Theory of Change The Together Culture theory of change emerged through co-design in 2022 in which 150 people participated.
Think of it as a future backwards plan. The impact we aim to have by 2033 is to tangibly create a more inclusive and ecological economy in Cambridge.
Three outcomes (the circles) indicate our impact and shape our plan. The arrows in between represent the products and services that we’re iteratively co-creating with our members to deliver those outcomes.

data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Together Culture is a community interest company based at 5 Fitzroy Street. We do what we say on the tin, we build together culture. Think of ‘Together Culture’ as a noun.
Together Culture (n.) the product of turning up to collaborate in the acts of sharing, caring, learning, and experimenting which results in the spreading of gritty hope, through action.
You're capable of helping to shape an economy that is more inclusive and ecological. At Together Culture, we're shaping a world of work that supports everyone's wellbeing and shares prosperity.
